Before you comment to check the tag #blacklivesmatter tell me what you see now.

This SUNDAY I will be a guest speaker at the “All things Lace” class which will be taken place in Columbus, OH at 12-6pm EST! I will be sharing some of my secrets in regards to my Online Business @luxus.label ❤️ and advice for future business owners. 

I hope you all are ready to learn some new tricks! @ohemma_j will be sharing the things she’s learned over the past 10+ years! A Celebrity Hair Vendor will be shared as well! 

Last but not least the First 10 people to sign up will be added to a drawing for a FREE MAKEOVER (New wig, New outfit, & Free Makeup appointment) 

Please feel free to email at touchedbytina1@gmail.com or DM us with any questions and or concerns before committing! 

All deposits can be made through the link in her bio!

node.text:
Luxus Dump 🎉
Yesterday I reached my highest day of sales and this is only the beginning! This is all GOD and hard work! In January I told myself and God I’m going to stop playing with my potential and take my business serious. Since then I’ve hit every single goal I set for myself. Now I’m doing double digit months easy and headed to 6 figure months soon! This hustle is personal if you know my story! This is just a glimpse of the behind the scenes 😩 I literally work 24/8 and still have a whole career. I want to show you guys my journey so that I can at least inspire a young black girl out there who wants to start a business! It can be done!👋🏾💕
@luxus.label 
#futuremillionaire #blessedandgrateful
